metadata.name: Interlude in Moonlight
metadata.description:
Interlude in Moonlight

My duality in self
is also that of my love
Caresses in the warmth of day
arms encircled in moonlight
My balance is found 
My love swells
tender moments 
now immortalized
in memory, in time,
I am enraptured.
